           SPELL=double-conversion
         VERSION=3.4.0
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:9a6f43497a772c78660d0c0f9bc42902f5cb99066a08f0ab50345db37ddf62bb491ae7f5ca45819251e3a1d41282e5646b269e912cbd24eca6b440a31409712f
          SOURCE=$SPELL-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/$SPELL-$VERSION
       WEB_SITE=https://github.com/google/$SPELL
   SOURCE_URL[0]=$WEB_SITE/archive/v$VERSION.tar.gz
      LICENSE[0]=BSD
         ENTERED=20180307
        KEYWORDS=""
           SHORT="binary<->decimal routines for IEEE doubles"
cat << EOF
double-conversion provides binary-decimal and decimal-binary routines for IEEE 
doubles.
The library consists of efficient conversion routines that have been extracted from 
the V8 JavaScript engine. The code has been refactored and improved so that it can be 
used more easily in other projects.
EOF
